'''''In Defiance of Existence''''' is the fifth [[studio album]] by [[Norway|Norwegian]] <!-- DO NOT CHANGE GENRE WITHOUT DISCUSSING ON TALK PAGE!!!! --> [[Symphonic Black Metal]] band [[Old Man's Child]], released on January 20, 2003.

== Track listing ==
All music and lyrics written and composed by Galder, except on tracks 4 & 7 music by Galder/Jardar.
